  "body": "here my scenario:\r\n- first i installed my chart using:  \r\n`helm install ./my-example-chart.tgz  --set key1=value1`\r\n- then i introduced new variable in my helm chart and i put it to my values.yaml file with default value.\r\n- i again created chart and used this command: \r\n`helm upgrade my-existing-chart ./my-example-chart.tgz --reuse-values`\r\n\r\nafter upgrade i see that helm doesn't pick new introduced values it only uses old key-value which is (key1-value1) from first installation.\r\n\r\ni was expecting even i supply reuse-values helm should pick new introduced key-value pairs from values.yaml file",
